    "Name": "Balar BL1-OR",
    "Details": "The <i>Balar</i> was designed by Luthien Armor Works and released alongside the <i>Avatar</i> as a competitor to the Inner Sphere's first OmniMech design. While the <i>Avatar</i> was based upon the clan's <i>Vulture</i> OmniMech, the <i>Balar</i> took cues from the <i>Ebon Jaguar</i> instead. Sporting an impressive 350-rated XL fusion engine, the <i>Balar</i> was fast for a 70-ton 'Mech, but prohibitively expensive, which ultimately caused the design to be mostly overlooked by Combine procurement agents.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Narrow/Low Profile</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.05</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Omni</color>\n\n",
